category: BROADWAY MUSICAL SETTINGS
category comment: 

clue: This show takes place on a Greek isle while a single mother prepares for her daughter's wedding

response: Mamma Mia!

clue: "The Music Man" takes place "right here in" this fictional Iowa city

response: River City

clue: This musical opens with Anna's arrival in Bangkok

response: The King and I

clue: The Middle Eastern town of Agrabah (which is almost an anagram of Baghdad)

response: Aladdin

clue: The '60s-set "Hairspray" takes place in this American city

response: Baltimore

